display

Enum WorldTile

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<WorldTile>
      • display.WorldTile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<WorldTile>

    public enum WorldTile
extends java.lang.Enum<WorldTile>
    This is a more complex enum that contains the tiles for the world. Each constant has an ID, an image, and an isSolid property. The world is rendered based on these properties.
